Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:37.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,-加油  加油  -加油  加油\N{\rENG}- Go, go, go! - Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:55.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,天吶\N{\rENG}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:09.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,別哭\N{\rENG}Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:13.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,別讓他們看到你哭  海莉\N{\rENG}Don't let 'em see you cry, Haley.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:15.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,下次你就會打敗他們\N{\rENG}You will get them next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:20.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,知道嗎  因為你是什麼來著\N{\rENG}All right? 'Cause what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:25.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是什麼\N{\rENG}What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:27.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,頂級掠食者\N{\rENG}The apex predator.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:28.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\rENG}Yeah, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:31.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,永遠都是頂級掠食者\N{\rENG}Apex predator. All day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:38.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad1}來電\N貝絲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:40.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,-怎麼了  -沒出什麼事吧\N{\rENG}- Hey, what's up? - Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:42.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,我給你打了一早上電話\N{\rENG}I've been calling you all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:44.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,抱歉  昨晚睡得晚  早起又要訓練\N{\rENG}Sorry. Late night, early practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:47.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們刮颶風也要訓練\N{\rENG}You're having practice during a hurricane?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,超過一百萬人\N{\rENG}More than one million people
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:51.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad1}重大新聞\N颶風溫蒂降臨佛羅裡達州
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:53.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,收到了強制疏散令\N{\rENG}now facing mandatory evacuation orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:55.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,預報說刮不到我們這裡\N{\rENG}They said it was gonna miss us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:56.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,你沒收到手機上的警報嗎\N{\rENG}Don't you get alerts on your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:58.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,這次颶風分級很高\N{\rENG}It's gonna hit really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:00.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,-路易  寶貝  -小兄弟  瞧瞧你\N{\rENG}- Louie, honey. - Hey, bubba. Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:04.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,話說回來  海莉  你有爸的消息嗎\N{\rENG}Anyway, Haley, listen. Have you heard from Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:05.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒有  怎麼了\N{\rENG}No. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:07.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,他不接我電話\N{\rENG}He's not answering my calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,他可能也熬夜了\N{\rENG}Well, he probably had a late night too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:11.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,我就是想確認一下他的安全\N{\rENG}Yeah, I just need to know he's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:13.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,政府已經讓整個南岸的人都撤離了\N{\rENG}They've already evacuated the whole south coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:15.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許他早就離開了\N{\rENG}Well, maybe he left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,也可能是在做什麼傻事\N{\rENG}Or maybe he's doing something stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:17.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,比方說硬挺到颶風過去\N{\rENG}like trying to ride it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:18.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,你瞭解他的脾氣\N{\rENG}You know what he's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:21.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,媽怎麼說的\N{\rENG}Well, what does Mom say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:23.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,媽在巴黎\N{\rENG}Mom's in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:26.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,和白馬王子在一起嗎\N{\rENG}With Prince Charming?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:27.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,別調侃她了\N{\rENG}Give her a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:29.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,爸現在應該回我電話了\N{\rENG}Dad should've returned my calls by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:30.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,他總是及時回電的\N{\rENG}He always does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:33.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,好  我開車去看看他\N{\rENG}Look, I'll drive down and check on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:35.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,-你瘋了嗎  -75號公路南向應該沒車\N{\rENG}- Are you crazy? - 75 South will be empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:37.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,我兩小時內就能趕到\N{\rENG}I can be there in, like, two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,我可不能讓你們兩個都困在五級颶風裡\N{\rENG}I'm not having both of you down there in a Category 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:41.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,那你為什麼打電話給我\N{\rENG}Then why did you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:43.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,我以為你可能有他的消息\N{\rENG}Because I thought you might have heard from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:44.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,我沒有\N{\rENG}Well, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:46.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,有一陣子沒有了\N{\rENG}Not for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:49.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,-你們又吵架了嗎  -是他跟我吵\N{\rENG}- Did you fight again? - He fights with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:51.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為你們倆一模一樣\N{\rENG}Because you're exactly alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:53.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,對  你更像媽媽\N{\rENG}Yeah, and you're more like Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:56.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,置身事外的感同身受\N{\rENG}Empathetic from a safe distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:04:59.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,行  當我沒說\N{\rENG}Okay, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:01.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,-貝絲  我得走了  -注意安全\N{\rENG}- Beth, I gotta go. - Stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:02.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,有他的消息就給我發短信\N{\rENG}If you hear from him, text me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:04.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,-好  我愛你  -我也愛你\N{\rENG}- Okay. I love you. - Love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:07.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,-再見  -再見  小可愛\N{\rENG}- Bye. - Bye, little cutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:11.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,時速可能達到241公里\N{\rENG}...maybe 150 miles per hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:14.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,這太可笑了  肯定是假的\N{\rENG}That is ridiculous. That can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:17.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,你要是覺得那個滑稽的話  聽聽這個\N{\rENG}I'm telling you, if you think that's funny, get this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:18.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,-說  -帕斯科縣的\N{\rENG}- Go ahead. - Pasco County
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:20.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,治安官辦公室已經警告群眾\N{\rENG}sheriff's office have warned people
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:22.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,不要向颶風開槍\N{\rENG}to not shoot guns into the hurricane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:24.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼  不能對颶風開槍\N{\rENG}What? You can't shoot guns in a hurricane?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:25.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,那很危險\N{\rENG}Well, it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:28.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(380,235)\bord0\shad0}民眾在與他人發生對抗時無需選擇退讓\N可在認為生命安全遭受威脅時使用致命武力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:28.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,畢竟佛羅裡達州有"不退讓法"\N{\rENG}Florida is a stand-your-ground state after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:31.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,說得沒錯  所以我才住在這裡\N{\rENG}Hell yeah, it is! That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:31.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad1}鱷魚養殖場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:36.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad1}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:39.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,你已接通戴夫·凱勒建築公司  戴夫·凱勒的電話\N{\rENG}You've reached Dave Keller, Dave Keller Construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:42.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,我可能正在哪個工地上  請留言\N{\rENG}Probably up a ladder somewhere, so please leave a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:46.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,爸  我是海莉  回我電話\N{\rENG}Dad, it's Haley. Call me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:49.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,貝絲很擔心你\N{\rENG}Beth's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:53.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,說完了\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:57.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,天吶  這都什麼事\N{\rENG}Oh, man. What a shit show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:01.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,我對天發誓  要是你早就走了\N{\rENG}I swear to God, if you've already left...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:12.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,減速  減速  減速 \N{\rENG}Slow down. Slow down, slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,抱歉  女士  我們不能讓你...\N{\rENG}Sorry, miss, we can't let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:19.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,海莉  你好啊\N{\rENG}Haley! What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:20.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,韋恩\N{\rENG}Hey, Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:22.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,情況如何\N{\rENG}How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:26.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,不太好  撤離令把人們都逼瘋了\N{\rENG}We've had better days. The evacuation drives people nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:27.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,這傢伙企圖繞道走\N{\rENG}This guy tried to go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:29.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,今年沒人開颶風派對嗎\N{\rENG}No hurricane party this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:31.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,應該沒有\N{\rENG}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:33.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,你姐姐還好嗎\N{\rENG}Hey, how's your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:35.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,你爸說她住在波士頓\N{\rENG}Your old man says she's living up in Boston.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:36.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,對  她挺好的\N{\rENG}Yeah. Yeah, she's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:39.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,其實就是她讓我去看看我爸的情況\N{\rENG}She actually asked me to go check on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,恐怕我不能讓你過去\N{\rENG}I'm afraid I can't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:46.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,風暴正轉向西邊  沖著我們來呢\N{\rENG}The storm's turning west and heading straight for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:47.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,-我們不能放人過去  -拜託  韋恩\N{\rENG}- We're not letting anyone through. - Come on, Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:49.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,他不接電話\N{\rENG}He's not answering his phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:50.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,我熟悉道路\N{\rENG}Look, I know the roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:52.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,我去看一眼馬上就回來  我保證\N{\rENG}I'll be in and out, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:58.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,真抱歉  海莉  我也想幫你  但我\N{\rENG}I'm really sorry, Haley. I wish I could help you out, but I just.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:01.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不能  我不想讓你受傷\N{\rENG}I can't. I wouldn't want you to get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:03.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,好  我理解\N{\rENG}Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:06.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,你回頭有機會能去看看他嗎\N{\rENG}Maybe you could check on him later if you get a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:08.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,-好  我盡力  -謝謝\N{\rENG}- Sure, I'll try. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:09.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,路上小心\N{\rENG}Drive safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,替我向你姐姐問好\N{\rENG}Say hi to your sister for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:15.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,-好的  -好\N{\rENG}- Sure. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:20.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,掉頭\N{\rENG}Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad1}道路被水淹沒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:35.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad1}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:37.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,去它的\N{\rENG}Fuck it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:42.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,停車\N{\rENG}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:46.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,前方所有道路禁止通行\N{\rENG}All roads are closed up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,請回話\N{\rENG}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:49.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,停車\N{\rENG}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:52.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,請原地等待\N{\rENG}Just wait! Stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:55.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,颶風溫蒂預計將\N{\rENG}It looks like Wendy's now gonna go
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:56.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,橫穿本州\N{\rENG}right through the middle of our state.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:07:59.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們強烈敦促當地居民\N{\rENG}We strongly urge local residents
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:01.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,聽取所有的官方警告\N{\rENG}to listen to all warnings from officials.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果你處於疏散區  你一定要撤離\N{\rENG}If you're in an evacuation zone, you gotta get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:05.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,一分鐘都別等\N{\rENG}You can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:08.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們  我們無力救援你們\N{\rENG}We... we won't be able to come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:12.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,我希望本州的每個家長都在思考\N{\rENG}I hope every parent in the state is thinking,
