Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:54.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,爸\N{\rENG}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:07.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,爸\N{\rENG}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:10.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,爸\N{\rENG}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:14.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,你好  糖糖\N{\rENG}Hi. Hey, Sugar.
