Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.59,0:48:29.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,皮特  收到了嗎\N{\rENG}Pete, you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.84,0:48:30.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,皮特  收到了嗎\N{\rENG}Pete, do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.35,0:48:36.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,皮特  該死的  你在哪\N{\rENG}Pete, goddamn it, man. Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.81,0:48:38.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,我需要你拿個套桿進來\N{\rENG}I need you down here now with a snare pole!
