Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.68,0:49:11.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,海莉  救我\N{\rENG}Haley, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.76,0:49:13.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,韋恩\N{\rENG}Wayne!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.52,0:49:21.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,抓住我的手\N{\rENG}Grab my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.69,0:50:04.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,我抓住你了\N{\rENG}I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.40,0:50:08.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,我沒能救下他\N{\rENG}I couldn't save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.03,0:50:17.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒事了\N{\rENG}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.08,0:50:21.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒事了  它們進不來\N{\rENG}It's okay. They can't get in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.08,0:50:23.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們在這裡很安全\N{\rENG}We're safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.84,0:50:27.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,爸\N{\rENG}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.92,0:50:28.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.47,0:50:32.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒事了\N{\rENG}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.84,0:50:33.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒事了\N{\rENG}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.35,0:50:43.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,我從沒想過會這樣死\N{\rENG}I never thought it would end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.73,0:50:46.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們就不該回來\N{\rENG}We should never have come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.27,0:50:48.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,海莉  堅強點\N{\rENG}Haley, you stay strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.44,0:50:50.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們會出去的\N{\rENG}We're getting out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.20,0:51:03.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,還記得你小時候\N{\rENG}You remember when you were little,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.33,0:51:06.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,貝絲能憋氣遊到游泳池另一頭\N{\rENG}and Beth could hold her breath for the length
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.29,0:51:07.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,而你不能嗎\N{\rENG}of the pool and you couldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.71,0:51:11.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,我現在並不想感懷往事  爸\N{\rENG}I'm not really up for memory lane right now, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.40,0:51:15.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,你那時特別生氣  大發脾氣\N{\rENG}Yeah, well, you got so mad and you stormed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.13,0:51:17.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒錯  我是個小混蛋\N{\rENG}Yeah, I was a little jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.51,0:51:19.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,海莉  那天晚上\N{\rENG}Yeah, well, Haley, that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.64,0:51:22.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,我淩晨兩點左右醒來\N{\rENG}I woke up about 2:00 in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.89,0:51:24.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為我聽到外面有動靜\N{\rENG}'cause I heard something outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.52,0:51:26.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,我以為是小偷  所以我偷偷下樓\N{\rENG}I thought it was a burglar, so I snuck down,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.40,0:51:28.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,結果看到你在游泳池裡\N{\rENG}and I saw you in the pool,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.52,0:51:31.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,一遍又一遍地加深呼吸\N{\rENG}taking your giant breaths again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.19,0:51:35.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,然後你做到了  海莉\N{\rENG}And you did it, Haley.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.95,0:51:38.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,你自己弄明白了怎麼做\N{\rENG}You figured that shit out all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.16,0:51:45.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,那時我就知道  這孩子是個鬥士\N{\rENG}And that's when I knew, this kid's a fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.42,0:51:50.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們或許倔強  但我們絕不放棄\N{\rENG}So we may be stubborn, but we do not give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.38,0:51:55.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,你放棄了媽媽\N{\rENG}You gave up on Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.43,0:51:59.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,你媽並不快樂  我那時自私\N{\rENG}Mom was not happy, and I was selfish,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.64,0:52:01.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,對她關心不夠\N{\rENG}and I didn't pay enough attention to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.60,0:52:03.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,-因為我  -不\N{\rENG}- Because of me. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.02,0:52:05.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,是的  因為你總陪著我\N{\rENG}Yes, because you were always with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.19,0:52:08.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,每個週末去比賽\N{\rENG}Every weekend at the meets.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.52,0:52:10.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,奔波在離開家的路上\N{\rENG}On the road away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.31,0:52:13.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,和你沒有關系  你真那麼想嗎\N{\rENG}It had nothing to do with you. Is that what you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.20,0:52:24.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為你和貝絲我們才沒有分開\N{\rENG}It was you and Beth that kept us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.66,0:52:28.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們離開後  我們就是...\N{\rENG}When you girls left, we were just...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.71,0:52:34.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,空蕩蕩的大房子裡的兩個孤獨的人\N{\rENG}two lonely people in a big, empty house.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.34,0:52:37.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,假裝美滿都沒人看\N{\rENG}Nobody to even pretend for.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.51,0:52:41.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,你媽有了重來的機會  海莉\N{\rENG}Your mom got a second chance, Haley,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.55,0:52:43.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,她值得擁有幸福\N{\rENG}and she deserves to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.60,0:52:45.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,你也是\N{\rENG}So do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.73,0:52:49.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不認為我值得\N{\rENG}I don't think I deserve one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.82,0:52:54.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想你\N{\rENG}I miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.36,0:52:58.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想念獲勝時看到你在看臺上\N{\rENG}I miss seeing your face in the stands when I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.99,0:53:00.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,你為什麼不再來了\N{\rENG}Why don't you come anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.16,0:53:03.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,-我以為你生我的氣了  -我確實生氣了\N{\rENG}- I thought you were mad at me. - I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.41,0:53:05.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rENG}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.31,0:53:29.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們會打敗這些無腦蜥蜴怪的\N{\rENG}We are gonna beat these pea-brained lizard shits.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.52,0:53:30.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,你和我\N{\rENG}You and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.02,0:53:35.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,之前我敲管道讓它們很不爽\N{\rENG}They didn't like it when I was banging on the pipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.15,0:53:38.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想我能分散它們的注意力\N{\rENG}I think I can distract them if you can dive
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.94,0:53:41.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果你能潛水一路遊到樓梯\N{\rENG}all the way under until you get to the stairs.
