Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.95,0:53:45.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎\N{\rENG}You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.58,0:53:47.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.54,0:53:50.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會回來救你的\N{\rENG}I'm coming back for you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.62,0:53:51.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,你最好回來\N{\rENG}You'd better.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.67,0:53:55.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.78,0:54:27.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.12,0:54:49.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\rENG}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.28,0:57:11.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,爸\N{\rENG}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.61,0:57:13.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,我無法到樓梯那去\N{\rENG}I can't make it to the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.21,0:57:18.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要去排水管試試\N{\rENG}I'm going for the drainpipe, okay?
