Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.92,1:05:58.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,快啊\N{\rENG}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.04,1:06:04.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,太好了  爸爸  太好了\N{\rENG}Yes, Daddy, yes! Yes!
