Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.07,1:06:37.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,起來  我們去開車\N{\rENG}Come on. Let's get to the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.19,1:06:48.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,該死\N{\rENG}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.23,1:06:50.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是吧\N{\rENG}No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.97,1:06:56.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,爸  我們怎麼辦\N{\rENG}Dad, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.51,1:07:05.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,有船  看到那邊了嗎\N{\rENG}Boat! You see over there?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.73,1:07:08.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,不  鱷魚太多了  我們得待在這裡\N{\rENG}No, there are too many of 'em. We need to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.31,1:07:10.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,不  堤壩會崩塌的\N{\rENG}No, those levees are gonna break,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.78,1:07:12.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們得在那之前離開\N{\rENG}and when they do we can't be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.21,1:07:15.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,那條船是我們離開的唯一機會\N{\rENG}That boat's our only chance to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.63,1:07:17.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們應該能過去\N{\rENG}I think we can make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.59,1:07:19.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\rENG}It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.09,1:07:25.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,它們聚在洪水中  因為那樣更容易捕獵\N{\rENG}They gather in the floodwaters 'cause it's easier to hunt.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.21,1:07:26.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,有水花它們就去追捕\N{\rENG}They hunt what splashes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.46,1:07:30.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,所以不濺起水花  就不會被追捕\N{\rENG}So no splashing, no hunting.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.66,1:07:34.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,雨能掩護我們\N{\rENG}I think the rain should cover us.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.81,1:07:35.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.28,1:07:39.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,來吧  狗狗\N{\rENG}Come on, girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.27,1:07:43.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒事的\N{\rENG}It's okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.19,1:08:53.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,暴風中心在我們上方\N{\rENG}The eye is above us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.42,1:09:05.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們最好快點\N{\rENG}We'd better hurry.
