Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.06,1:09:33.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,海莉  你得遊過去\N{\rENG}Haley, you need to swim.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.20,1:09:38.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,你能行的  你比它們快\N{\rENG}You got this! You're faster than they are!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.87,1:09:40.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是什麼\N{\rENG}What are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.95,1:09:42.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,快遊\N{\rENG}Swim!
